case.title: Looking for commitment,and get married - 33 (ny)
case.text: I want to find someone to have a family. I want to settle and get.married. I am 33 and I think this is the time to have someone to sspend times with.I need a romantic,honest, athletic,professional man.Non smoker,independent and only men with no kids. I like to travel,spend times together,so please have some free times for us,im not interestedin no busy man .
